data.description: Situated in the beautiful Highlands Stirling subdivision, near Loch Lomond and less than a mile from the Lakepoint Marina and Restaurant, near bike trails, Highlands golf course, and the Branchwood recreation center. Unique split floor plan with open living area, vaulted ceilings, solar tubes and wood burning marble fireplace. Granite countertops, custom tile backsplash behind range, and tiled kitchen and bathrooms. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, large 24x24 garage and 12x14 study or 4th bedroom. New roof in 2020.
